ca.ualberta.trinkettrader.Friends

Class FriendsInventoryController

  • java.lang.Object
    • ca.ualberta.trinkettrader.Friends.FriendsInventoryController

  • public class FriendsInventoryController
extends java.lang.Object
    Controller for handling interactions from the FriendsInventoryActivity. The controller manages clicks on the trinkets, which connects the user to the TrinketDetailsActivity.
